=09=09=09=09I=01,m all right, Jack
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09After losing out in the race to succeed Jack Welch at General E=
lectric, two=20
top executives departed. Robert Nardelli, in charge of GE Power Systems, wi=
ll=20
become chief executive at Home Depot, an American DIY retailer. And James=
=20
McNerney, head of GE Aircraft Engines, will take up the chief executive=01,=
s=20
role at 3M, a diversified manufacturer. Shares in both companies shot up.
